307
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:11,590
Ziying.

308
00:18:12,680 --> 00:18:14,960
Let's talk here.

309
00:18:15,930 --> 00:18:16,730
Grandmaster,

310
00:18:17,730 --> 00:18:18,460
